# ============================================================
# CIVILIZATION COMPATIBILITY HANDLING FLOW
# ============================================================

status: canonical
layer: 050.flow
system: civilization-os
owner: Boss
prepared_by: Zero

purpose:
Define the canonical compatibility handling flow.

flow_steps:
1 contract version is inspected
2 compatibility status is resolved
3 contract is classified as compatible, limited, or incompatible
4 compatible contract continues
5 limited contract continues under bounded handling
6 incompatible contract is rejected or isolated

compatibility_rule:
Consumers must not guess missing compatibility semantics.
